Author: sunflowertattoos
Text: I've been there too. Hell, I might even be there tomorrow. But all these negative thoughts are warped and keeping you from seeing that people do care about you. PM me if you feel like it ever

Author: Sal4Sale
Text: It’s easy to feel invisible, especially at school. The feeling of being ignored is awful. But you aren’t insignificant, nobody is. If you want to chat, PM me, I’m free to talk if you need to vent.
